   Army: 800-233-5259, or 800-468-7786 in Virginia.
   Navy: 800-523-2975, or 800-572-2126 in Virginia.
   Air Force: 800-531-5501, or 800-292-5642 in Texas.
   Marines: 202-694-1492.
