and her baby, two sheep, two goats, reindeer and a miniature
donkey,'' Hanna said.
   But the network said there would not ``be any Christmas animals
today because we're at war with Panama,'' Hanna said.
   ``I never did like that SOB Noriega; now I hate him.''
