<TEXT>
   The Grinches who stole Victor Diaz's van were
too busy guzzling two six-packs of beer he left on a front seat to
notice a load of Christmas toys in the back worth more than $500.
   ``My jaws dropped when I saw the toys in there,'' Diaz said
